1. *Kazna* će biti isplaćena u roku od mesec dana. (The penalty will be paid within a month.)
2. On je upozorio da će biti *kazne* za nepoštovanje zakona. (He warned that there will be penalties for disobeying the law.)
3. Nije bilo *kazne* za prekršaj. (There was no penalty for the offence.)
4. Ona je zbog prekršaja dobila *kaznu*. (She was given a penalty for the offence.)
5. *Kaznio* sam ga za laž. (I punished him for lying.)